# A3: an UNREACHABLE server during the pre-launch save check (engine exit 3) must launch
# silently with the local save and log action=offline — never "no server saves". The
# 2026-07-02 Smart Pro field session: tailscaled never came up, --list-saves printed nothing
# with rc=0, and the pak showed "No server saves for ✓ Pokemon Emerald" while both
# revisions sat on the server.
desc fetch hook: list-saves unreachable (rc=3) -> silent launch, honest action=offline log
invoke prehook
config paired
romarg Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
sdfile+ Roms/Game Boy Advance (GBA)/✓ Zelda.gba
engine 3|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace ENGINE --list-saves
expect_trace_absent LIST[
expect_trace_absent ENGINE --restore-save
expect_log newest=none action=offline
